OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBP scales back climate     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftargets as profits hit     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frecord                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy giant BP has reported record    
OL,6, annual profits as it scaled back plans 
OL,7, to reduce the amount of oil and gas it 
OL,8, produces by 2030.                      
OL,10,FThe company's profits more than doubled
OL,11,Fto $27.7bn (#23bn) in 2022, as energy  
OL,12,Fprices soared after Russia invaded     
OL,13,FUkraine.                               
OL,15,FOther energy firms have seen similar   
OL,16,Frises, with Shell reporting record     
OL,17,Fearnings of nearly $40bn last week.    
OL,19,FIt has led to calls for energy firms to
OL,20,Fpay more tax as people's bills soar.   
